[Student "S"]
{The bidding has been as shown.   

Wow! Great \S support and 15 points. You cue-bid 2\D, forcing partner to bid. He says 2\S. Your turn. 

Partner has not made a strong bid and it is possible that 10 tricks will be too high. But it is pretty likely that game can be made so you bid it. Be bold!}

